{"id":4874,"created":1449242852,"modified":1449242852,"data":{"arcane_focus_component":"0","area":"","casting_time":"1 standard action","corrupt_component":"0","description_html":"\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eYour dragonmark grows warm. Dangerous animals nearby no longer regard you as a threat.\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eFor the duration of the spell, no animal threatens or attacks you unless you attack it first. The spell\u0026#39;s duration depends on the strength of your dragonmark.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctable\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cth\u003eDragonmark \u003c/th\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cth\u003eDuration \u003c/th\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e Least \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e 1 min./level \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e Lesser \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e 10 min./level \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e Greater or Siberys \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003ctd\u003e 1 hour/level \u003c/td\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/tr\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/table\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you attack any animal, the spell ends immediately.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003c/b\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cem\u003eDragonmark:\u003c/em\u003e Any true or aberrant dragonmark.\u003c/p\u003e","descriptors":"","divine_focus_component":"0","duration":"See text","effect":"","id":4874,"material_component":"0","meta_breath_component":"0","name":"Mark of the Wild","page":152,"rulebook":"Dragonmarked","saving_throw":"","school":"Transmutation","somatic_component":"1","spell_range":"Personal","spell_resistance":"","subschool":"","target":"You","true_name_component":"0","verbal_component":"1","xp_component":"0"}}